{"tha-ap442:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap442:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap442:0.3":"10 Ambaphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap442:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap442:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap442:1.3":"Pindaya vicarantassa, ","tha-ap442:1.4":"dharato uttamam yasam. ","tha-ap442:2.1":"Aggaphalam gahetvana, ","tha-ap442:2.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap442:2.3":"Dakkhineyyassa virassa, ","tha-ap442:2.4":"adasim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap442:3.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap442:3.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap442:3.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap442:3.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap442:4.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap442:4.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap442:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap442:4.4":"aggadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap442:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap442:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap442:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap442:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap442:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap442:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap442:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap442:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap442:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap442:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ambaphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap442:9.1":"Ambaphaliyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap442:10.1":"Ekaviharivaggo catucattalisamo. ","tha-ap442:11.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap442:12.1":"Thero ekavihari ca, ","tha-ap442:12.2":"sankhiyo patihirako; ","tha-ap442:12.3":"Thaviko ucchukhandi ca, ","tha-ap442:12.4":"kalambaambatakado. ","tha-ap442:13.1":"Haritakambapindi ca, ","tha-ap442:13.2":"ambado dasamo yati; ","tha-ap442:13.3":"Chalasiti ca gathayo, ","tha-ap442:13.4":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}